prime_award_base_transaction_description: DATA GOVERNANCE AND ANALYTICS SUPPORT SERVICES
subawardee_business_types: MINORITY-OWNED BUSINESS,SELF-CERTIFIED SMALL DISADVANTAGED BUSINESS,FOR-PROFIT ORGANIZATION,ECONOMICALLY DISADVANTAGED WOMEN-OWNED SMALL BUSINESS,WOMAN-OWNED BUSINESS,ASIAN-PACIFIC AMERICAN OWNED,S CORPORATION
subaward_description: THE PURPOSE OF THIS PROJECT IS TO SUPPORT THE OFFICE OF CHIEF FINANCIAL OFFICER (OFCO) TO DEVELOP A SUSTAINABLE AND EXPANSIVE DATA GOVERNANCE, MANAGEAND AND ANALYTICS (DGMA) PROGRAM THAT IDENTIFIES AND CAPTURES THE MOST VALUE AND MEANINGFUL INSIGHTS FROM DATA AND TURN THEM INTO COMPETITIVE ADVANTAGES FOR THE OCFO. THIS INCLUDES PROVIDING PROGRAM MANAGEMENT FOR THE ENTIRE PROGRAM TEAM THROUGHOUT THE LIFE OF THE TASK ORDER, SUPPORTING THE DEVELOPMENT AND ADMINISTRATION OF AN OFCO DATA GOVERNANCE IMPLEMENTATION ROADMAP, AND PROVIDING ADMINISTRATIVE SUPPORT.

subawardee_business_types: MINORITY-OWNED BUSINESS,SELF-CERTIFIED SMALL DISADVANTAGED BUSINESS,FOR-PROFIT ORGANIZATION,ECONOMICALLY DISADVANTAGED WOMEN-OWNED SMALL BUSINESS,WOMAN-OWNED BUSINESS,ASIAN-PACIFIC AMERICAN OWNED,S CORPORATION
subaward_description: THE PURPOSE OF THIS PROJECT IS TO SUPPORT THE OFFICE OF CHIEF FINANCIAL OFFICER (OFCO) TO DEVELOP A SUSTAINABLE AND EXPANSIVE DATA GOVERNANCE, MANAGEAND AND ANALYTICS (DGMA) PROGRAM THAT IDENTIFIES AND CAPTURES THE MOST VALUE AND MEANINGFUL INSIGHTS FROM DATA AND TURN THEM INTO COMPETITIVE ADVANTAGES FOR THE OCFO. THIS INCLUDES PROVIDING PROGRAM MANAGEMENT FOR THE ENTIRE PROGRAM TEAM THROUGHOUT THE LIFE OF THE TASK ORDER, SUPPORTING THE DEVELOPMENT AND ADMINISTRATION OF AN OFCO DATA GOVERNANCE IMPLEMENTATION ROADMAP, AND PROVIDING ADMINISTRATIVE SUPPORT.
